description:
Live in sync with your cycle using Flo, the world’s most popular female health app. Get personalised insights and predictions on your body.

Whether you want to predict your period, get pregnant, track your pregnancy, or better understand your symptoms, Flo is your all-in-one female health partner. Join over 420 million members.

With Flo, you can:
- Keep your data safe: Flo is the first period and ovulation tracker to achieve dual ISO 27001 and ISO 27701 Certifications (aka gold standards in data protection).
- Feel more understood: Share your Flo insights via Flo for Partners to feel more connected, understood, and supported.
- Get an extra layer of protection: Anonymous Mode means no one, not even Flo, can identify you based on your health data.
- Join a supportive community: Secret Chats is where members can discuss topics and connect with others on the same journey.
- Access reliable health information: Flo collaborates with a globally recognised organisation dedicated to reproductive health and rights, ensuring trustworthy support for your health journey.

With Flo Premium, you can enjoy:
- Monthly cycle reports
- Symptom predictions and patterns
- Tailored prediction insights
- Detailed pregnancy tracking
- Full access to Flo for Partners
- A 24/7 virtual Health Assistant
- All articles, videos, and courses reviewed by 140+ health experts

New! Flo supports perimenopause:
- Know what might be perimenopause and how to tune in to your body’s changes.
- Get clarity on common perimenopause symptoms and what can help.
- Make more informed health decisions and identify what you need to feel your best.

Start tracking your cycle for free today.

Privacy Policy and Terms of Use:
https://flo.health/privacy-policy  
https://flo.health/terms-of-use 

Connect with Flo:
Web: flo.health
TikTok: @flotracker
Instagram: @flotracker

Please note: Flo is not a diagnostic tool and should not be used as a method of contraception or to facilitate conception. Predictions and insights provided by the app are intended for informational purposes only and are not a substitute for professional medical advice, diagnosis, or treatment. Always consult a qualified healthcare provider for any health concerns or decisions.

Flo uses HealthKit to read menstrual cycle data and export your Flo activities to the Health app.

If you have any difficulties using the app, contact Flo via support@flo.health.

Notice of Access Permission:
Flo may request permission for:
- In-app notifications or reminders.
- Uploading photos to specific forum discussions.
- Uploading audio recordings to closed group chats.
Content sharing is entirely optional. Flo does not automatically access your content. You can select what you want to share.

Fit Path: Your Ultimate Health & Fitness Companion

Start your wellness journey with Fit Path, the all-in-one app that helps you live a healthier, more balanced life. Whether you're building strength, improving nutrition, staying hydrated, or boosting mental clarity, Fit Path has everything you need to reach your fitness and health goals.

Support Your Wellness Journey

Fit Path helps you take care of your whole health—body, mind, and spirit. The app combines workouts, mindfulness, nutrition tracking, hydration reminders, and more, all in one place. Every feature is connected, so you can track your progress, stay consistent, and create healthy habits that fit your lifestyle. Whether you want to lose weight, gain strength, or reduce stress, Fit Path gives you the tools to succeed.

Personalized Plans for You

No two people are the same, so Fit Path gives you personalized plans. Whether it's workout routines, nutrition goals, or fasting schedules, the app adjusts based on your fitness level, preferences, and goals. Whether you're just starting out or aiming to take your fitness to the next level, Fit Path helps you progress at your own pace.

Stay Consistent and Motivated

Staying on track is key to success, and Fit Path makes it easy. The “Today” tab shows all your daily tasks in one place—workouts, meals, mindfulness, and hydration reminders. As you complete each task, you’ll see your progress and stay motivated. Daily reminders and habit tracking help you stay focused and consistent, ensuring you reach your goals.

Track Your Progress with Insights

Fit Path helps you understand your progress by tracking your fitness, nutrition, and hydration data. The app gives you useful feedback, helping you spot trends, celebrate your progress, and make improvements. Whether you're tracking weight loss, muscle gain, or general wellness, Fit Path ensures you're always on top of your health journey.

Easy to Use, For Everyone

Designed with simplicity in mind, Fit Path is easy to use for everyone, no matter your tech skills. Whether you're new to wellness apps or an experienced user, you'll find Fit Path intuitive and simple to navigate, so you can focus on what matters—your health.

Build Sustainable Health Habits

Healthy habits last a lifetime, and Fit Path helps you build them. With mindful eating, regular exercise, hydration, and stress management, the app helps you develop lasting routines that improve your overall health. Fit Path also offers expert tips, educational content, and personalized guidance, so you can make smarter choices every day.

Achieve Your Goals with Fit Path

Fit Path is your partner in achieving wellness. With custom fitness routines, mindfulness practices, meal tracking, and hydration reminders, the app gives you the tools you need to stay on track. Take control of your health and start your journey today. Download Fit Path and enjoy a healthier, more balanced life.

With Fit Path, every day is a step toward better health. Whether you're focusing on fitness, mental clarity, or overall wellness, Fit Path has everything you need to make lasting change. Start today and make living healthy easier and more enjoyable.

We provide 500+ easy asanas to help you achieve your health and fitness goals - lose weight; improve strength, balance, and flexibility; relieve stress and anxiety; feel alive and connected.

WHAT YOU’LL EXPERIENCE
• Guided Exercises: real-time tips on correct posture and breathing
• Personalized Workout Planner: custom plan based on your goals, fitness level, target areas, etc
• 3 Difficulty Levels: progress from beginner to advanced at your own pace
• Variety of Routines: explore yoga, pilates, stretching, and more
• Flexible Timing: sessions ranging from 5 to 14 minutes fit seamlessly into your schedule
• All Body Parts: focus on specific areas with precision, arms, legs, butt, and abs
• Home-Based: from morning stretching to bedtime relaxation, fit every part of your day

BEGINNER FRIENDLY
All you need is a mat and enough space to place it. With the detailed guidance from our app, you don't have to be an expert to reap the benefits. No matter your age and weight, this exercise is for everyone.

RICH MOVEMENT LIBRARY WITH COACHING TIPS
Tree Pose, Warrior, Bridge, Downward Dog…over 100 basic exercises with well-explained instructions in texts and videos will help you quickly get started and develop interests. Gentle voice tips with immersive relaxation music allow you to focus on your poses, breath, and mind without staring at the screen for instructions all the time.

QUICK DAILY STRETCHING ROUTINES
Havard Health indicated that stretching keeps the muscles flexible, strong, and healthy, and we need that flexibility to maintain a range of motion in joints. In our app, you can find many quick daily stretching routines to fit your needs, such as "Bedtime Stretch for SLEEP" or "Upper body stretching".

STRENGTHEN YOUR BODY AND MIND
More than burning calories and shaping muscles, this is also a practice for your mind. During workout, you'll combine physical exercise with meditation practice, which would help you get in tune with your body and your inner self. 
	
NATURALLY RELIEVE CHRONIC PAIN
Researchers believe that yoga can aid individuals coping with muscle tension, low back pain, and other chronic conditions. Furthermore, enhancing mood and mental health is also crucial. In this app, we offer diverse workouts tailored to meet these specific needs.

EXERCISE ANYTIME, ANYWHERE
By spending only 0.35% time of your day, you can be closer to better health. No equipment, no gym, our app makes it simple for you to complete a quick workout routine at home, at the office, in the park, or even when you're traveling. Get your body toned and shaped anytime, anywhere.

MIRROR WORKOUT TO A BIG SCREEN
Use AirPlay support to mirror your workout on the TV or a big screen for an immersive fitness experience.

TRACK YOUR FITNESS PROGRESS
Track your progress of daily challenges, and sync your data to Apple Health. You will see the changes in your weight and body shape. You will feel the lightness of your mind and spirit.

PulsePro can not only monitor heart rate, test mental health, record blood pressure, blood sugar and blood oxygen, but also output health reports through top AI technology, give advice on maintaining good health and recommend good eating habits.


Here's what makes PulsePro a must-have for your health journey:

- Effortless Heart Rate Monitoring: Simply place your finger on your phone's camera, and PulsePro does the rest. It detects and records your heart rate, providing instant feedback on your vital signs. With PulsePro, monitoring your health is always at your fingertips.


- AI Generated Health Report: Pulse Pro analyzes your health data through the latest AI technology and generates detailed and accurate health reports. AI will also give you advice on staying healthy and recommend good eating habits based on your health condition.


- Comprehensive Blood Pressure and Blood Sugar Tracking: Not only does PulsePro record your blood pressure and blood sugar, but it also presents your data in easy-to-understand charts. Track the latest trends in your health and make informed adjustments to your lifestyle.


- Recipe Week Plan: PulsePro not only provides weekly recipe plans for managing blood pressure, lowering blood sugar, and stabilizing heart rate, but also includes other recipe plans, such as weight loss recipe plans, etc. You can even develop your own exclusive recipes according to your needs plan.Immerse yourself in a week of balanced, nourishing meals with our Recipe Week Plan, and take a significant step towards enhanced health and well-being.


- Timely Health Reminders: Set reminders in PulsePro, and it will prompt you to conduct regular health checks. Staying on track with your health has never been easier.


- Test mental health: Complete a small number of mental health test questions, and PulsePro will analyze your answers through AI, give you mental health results and give you suggestions for maintaining good mental health.


- Food Analysis Guide: You can check the nutritional facts of common foods on PulsePro, and get food recommendations.


- Activity Capability Assessment：PulsePro leverages AI technology to analyze your activity data in depth, generating comprehensive health reports to help you enhance your overall well-being.


- Secure and Private: Protecting user data is our top priority. Our app ensures the privacy and security of all sensitive information, allowing users to confidently Monitor heart rate without worries.


How to Use PulsePro for Heart Rate Measurement:

- Ensure your fingers aren't too cold.

- Cover the camera lens and flash completely with your fingertip.

- Press gently – applying too much pressure can reduce blood flow and affect accuracy.


Important Notice:

- PulsePro is not designed for medical purposes.

- The app can only measure heart rate, but not blood pressure or blood sugar level.

- It serves as a source of general health information for recording purposes only.

- Always consult your doctor with any health concerns.


PulsePro is connected to HealthKit to sync and analyze your daily data.

What is WalkWork?

WalkWork is a step counter application where the more you walk, the more rewards you earn. You can exchange the rewarded energy for the rewards of your choice.

This step counter is completely free, and the activity tracker motivates you to walk. WalkWork converts your steps into 'StepEnergy' in the form of virtual energy to promote a healthier lifestyle. Everyone can use this energy to redeem various attractive rewards, such as popular gift cards.

The WalkWork app is entirely free, allowing you to obtain energy simply by walking or running. Our app's mission is to promote your health.


How to Use WalkWork?

Download the WalkWork app for free from the app store and launch it. After completing the setup process, start walking. Whenever you walk for a certain duration, you can claim unlocked energy blocks within the app.


Where Can You Collect Energy?

Home page treasure chests, newbie sign-ins, and daily stage rewards offer substantial rewards. Exchange the earned energy for gift cards (Amazon, Walmart, Sephora, eBay, Uber, etc.) and not only receive lucrative rewards but also improve your health.


How to Get StepEnergy？

Walking: Earn up to 100 energy units per day! When you reach 10,000 steps, all rewards will be unlocked and available for claiming!

Sign-In: Newbies can log in daily within the first seven days and receive energy. You can claim it at any time of the day!

Packs: Stage rewards are triggered when you reach a certain number of steps daily.

Lottery: The lucky wheel offers a chance to win up to 10,000 energy units.

The best part? All features are completely free!


Other Content

Big Wheel: Enjoy various free games in WalkWork. We regularly update new content.

Trend: Review your exercise history and trends for daily, seven-day, and thirty-day periods! WalkWork compiles your steps, calorie burn, exercise time, and walking distance, allowing you to track your progress.


Attention

·WalkWork aims to track or encourage a healthy work-life, which may help people with certain chronic diseases or conditions live better.

·WalkWork is not intended for diagnosing acute or chronic diseases or other conditions, nor for their treatment or prevention. Before starting any new lifestyle or fitness program, you should seek advice from a physician.

·WalkWork is currently available for use worldwide. When using it, please enable the relevant permissions on your device to avoid your device being flagged as high-risk by the risk control system, which could impede your ability to redeem rewards. Please avoid using VPNs or other proxies or emulators, otherwise your account may be restricted.

·Use of devices not meeting specifications and standards may be limited.

·Gift card information in WalkWork is provided solely for redemption information and user obligations and does not imply any affiliation with our company in any way.

HeartIn: Your Comprehensive Heart Health Companion

Welcome to HeartIn, the app designed to empower you to take control of your heart health with ease and precision. Utilizing cutting-edge technology, HeartIn transforms your smartphone into a powerful heart rate monitor, providing personalized insights and resources to help you lead a healthier lifestyle. From measuring your heart rate and variability to monitoring your stress and energy levels, HeartIn offers an all-in-one solution for your cardiovascular wellness.

Key Features

Heart Rate Measurement & Variability (HRV)
With HeartIn, measuring your heart rate is as simple as placing your finger over your smartphone's camera. Our innovative technology uses the camera and flash to detect subtle changes in light absorption, giving you accurate readings in just seconds.

Heart Score
After each measurement, receive a personalized heart score that evaluates your heart health based on age and gender benchmarks. HeartIn calculates this score with HRV (Heart Rate Variability) as its essential metric, integrating age and gender to provide a comprehensive view of your heart health.

HRV Graphs
Track your heart rate variability over time with intuitive line graphs, providing insights into your stress levels, recovery, and overall heart health.

Pulse Rate Monitoring
Seamlessly integrate with your Apple Watch for real-time pulse rate monitoring. This feature ensures you stay informed about your cardiovascular status throughout the day, helping you recognize patterns and make informed lifestyle choices.

Stress & Energy Monitoring
Understand how your daily activities impact your well-being with our stress and energy monitoring features. By analyzing your HRV, HeartIn provides daily insights and recommendations to help you manage stress and boost your energy levels effectively.

Blood Pressure & Blood Oxygen Logging
Easily log your blood pressure and oxygen saturation levels within the app. Track your readings over time with user-friendly history logs that visualize trends, allowing you to make informed decisions about your health.

AI Chatbot & Self-Care Resources
Engage with our health-focused AI chatbot for instant responses to your heart health queries. Explore a curated library of articles on heart health, wellness tips, and daily health insights, all tailored to support your journey towards a healthier lifestyle.

User-Centric Design
HeartIn is crafted with user experience in mind, featuring a clean and intuitive interface that allows for easy navigation between measurements, logs, and self-care resources. Whether you're a health enthusiast or just starting your wellness journey, HeartIn offers a seamless experience for everyone.

Conclusion
Take the first step towards better heart health with HeartIn. Whether you're monitoring your heart rate, managing stress, or exploring self-care resources, HeartIn is your trusted partner in health and wellness. Download HeartIn today and empower yourself with the knowledge and tools to lead a healthier life!
